{
  "name": "Charming Persona",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/fleur-de-lis-yellow.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Skill </p><p>You've mastered the art of charming those around you, gaining the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• You gain proficiency in the Persuasion skill.</p><p> If you are already proficient, you instead gain Mastery.</p><p>• You are skilled in gathering information through conversation, without asking a single question.</p><p> By spending 10 minutes gathering information in a new place, you become aware of all current rumors and potentially important people you should be on the lookout for.</p><p>• If you spend 1 minute talking to someone, you can make a Charisma (Persuasion) check contested by a creature's passive insight.</p><p> If you or your companions are in combat with the creature, you automatically fail.</p><p> On a success, the target gains 2 ranks of charmed for you as long as it remains within 60 feet of you for the next 10 minutes.</p><p></p>",
